{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act13side", "eventName": "長夜臨光", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "NL-1", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "金盞花", "storyInfo": "馬克維茨從麥基口中聽到了“零號地塊”的事情，大為動容，同時，在一場即將開始的比賽中，鏽銅騎士似乎對感染者對手別有用心。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_23_G03", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_212_1"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  留步，馬克維茨先生。", "name": "發言人麥基"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_212_1"}, {"id": 11, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_211_1#4", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  是您啊，麥基先生，您......您有事找我？", "name": "發言人馬克維茨"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_211_1#4"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_211_1#4", "name2": "avg_npc_212_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  又見面了，你收到聯合會的信件了嗎？", "name": "發言人麥基"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_212_1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  特錦賽期間負責賽事監督的發言人只有我們倆......這可是個苦差事，但也備受矚目。", "name": "發言人麥基"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_212_1"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  如果想要在摘掉“發言人”三個字之後還能繼續平步青雲，眼下這可是最好的機會了。", "name": "發言人麥基"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_212_1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_211_1#5", "name2": "avg_npc_212_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  哈哈......不怕您笑話，我寧可不被這麼矚目，去負責場地活動的策劃一類......", "name": "發言人馬克維茨"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_211_1#5"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_211_1#5", "name2": "avg_npc_212_1#3", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  您擅長這些？", "name": "發言人麥基"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_212_1#3"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_211_1#7", "name2": "avg_npc_212_1#3", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  可沒什麼擅長不擅長的，我只是......", "name": "發言人馬克維茨"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_211_1#7"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_211_1#7", "name2": "avg_npc_212_1#6", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  您又謙虛了，您適應得比那些老員工都快。", "name": "發言人麥基"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_212_1#6"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_211_1#7", "name2": "avg_npc_212_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ——不過今天找您，是有一些別的事情我想提前知會您一聲。", "name": "發言人麥基"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_212_1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  咱們找一間休息室聊吧？", "name": "發言人麥基"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_212_1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_211_1#3", "name2": "avg_npc_212_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  啊，聽您的......", "name": "發言人馬克維茨"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_211_1#3"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_23_G09", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_211_1", "name2": "avg_npc_212_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  什麼事需要這麼謹慎？", "name": "發言人馬克維茨"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_211_1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_211_1", "name2": "avg_npc_212_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  其實這些，本不該我來和您說，但是恰爾內先生走得匆忙。", "name": "發言人麥基"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_212_1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  卡瓦萊利亞基除了核心的大騎士領本土，每屆會從商業發展最迅速的城市中選出三座，合併成為如今的大騎士領。", "name": "發言人麥基"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_212_1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  在特錦賽結束之後的幾個月內，除了大騎士領外的移動城市，會根據航線工程師的設計，在一個月內回到原本的航線之中。", "name": "發言人麥基"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_212_1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_211_1", "name2": "avg_npc_212_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  每次四城合併都是一次機遇。可觀的人流量，無縫通商，以及......處理一些問題的機會。", "name": "發言人麥基"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_212_1#2"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  說實在的，要不是四城聯合的規模實在過於龐大，無法有效移動，躲避天災，也難處理物資分配和開採問題。", "name": "發言人麥基"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_212_1#2"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我真希望四城聯合永不解散。", "name": "發言人麥基"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_212_1#2"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_211_1", "name2": "avg_npc_212_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  不過今天要說的是一個......嗯......潛規則。", "name": "發言人麥基"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_212_1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_211_1#3", "name2": "avg_npc_212_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  是關於......？", "name": "發言人馬克維茨"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_211_1#3"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_211_1#3", "name2": "avg_npc_212_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......感染者。", "name": "發言人麥基"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_212_1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  梅什科工業集團今年為大騎士領提供了七個移動平台，相當於其他國家一座城區的規模......當然，這是檯面上的部分。", "name": "發言人麥基"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_212_1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_211_1#5", "name2": "avg_npc_212_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  這些，我都從同事那裡聽聞過。", "name": "發言人馬克維茨"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_211_1#5"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_211_1#5", "name2": "avg_npc_212_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  現在我們應當關注的重點是零號地塊。它不在梅什科工業交付的合法名單上。", "name": "發言人麥基"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_212_1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  這個地塊性質特殊，它是一個規模很小的移動平台，現在連接在西南邊角，十七號城區之外。", "name": "發言人麥基"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_212_1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_211_1#3", "name2": "avg_npc_212_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  那裡是......", "name": "發言人馬克維茨"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_211_1#3"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_211_1#3", "name2": "avg_npc_212_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  是的，那裡就在感染者收容治療中心旁邊。", "name": "發言人麥基"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_212_1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_211_1#3", "name2": "avg_npc_212_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  原諒我的無禮，馬克維茨先生，接下來我們交談的每一句話，都要錄影記錄。", "name": "發言人麥基"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_212_1#2"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_211_1#3", "name2": "avg_npc_212_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  這是規定......發言人之中不允許有任何背叛聯合會的行為。", "name": "發言人麥基"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_212_1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_211_1#3", "name2": "avg_npc_212_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......", "name": "發言人馬克維茨"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_211_1#3"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_211_1#5", "name2": "avg_npc_212_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......我明白了。", "name": "發言人馬克維茨"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_211_1#5"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_23_G03", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_211_1#5", "name2": "avg_npc_212_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......", "name": "發言人馬克維茨"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_211_1#5"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_211_1#5", "name2": "avg_npc_212_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  您的臉色很難看......我知道，我一開始聽說的時候，也是您這樣。", "name": "發言人麥基"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_212_1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_211_1#7", "name2": "avg_npc_212_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  可這也太不人道了......", "name": "發言人馬克維茨"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_211_1#7"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_211_1#7", "name2": "avg_npc_212_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......您現在是董事會的執行人，商業聯合會的發言人，馬克維茨兄。", "name": "發言人麥基"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_212_1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_211_1#7", "name2": "avg_npc_212_1#6", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......我只是提醒您這一點，當然，不是警告或是威脅什麼的——哈哈，恰爾內先生總會給人這樣的感覺對吧？", "name": "發言人麥基"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_212_1#6"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_211_1#7", "name2": "avg_npc_212_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  盡在把握，瞭若指掌。你不聽他的可不行。", "name": "發言人麥基"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_212_1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_211_1#5", "name2": "avg_npc_212_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......", "name": "發言人馬克維茨"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_211_1#5"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_211_1#5", "name2": "avg_npc_212_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我可沒那個意思，馬克維茨兄，我們得相互扶持。", "name": "發言人麥基"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_212_1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  您該好好想想我的話，我接下來還要去和幾個騎士團確認行程。", "name": "發言人麥基"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_212_1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  回頭見。", "name": "發言人麥基"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_212_1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_nearllivingroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_064_weapon_1#5"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......瑪恩納？", "name": "佐菲婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_064_weapon_1#5"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你在嗎？瑪——", "name": "佐菲婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_064_weapon_1#5"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_064_weapon_1"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#4", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......佐菲婭姑母？", "name": "瑪嘉烈"}, "figure_art": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#4"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#4", "name2": "avg_npc_064_weapon_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  啊......瑪嘉烈，你怎麼還在家裡？", "name": "佐菲婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_064_weapon_1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  瑪莉婭那孩子不是說你去騎士協會了嗎？", "name": "佐菲婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_064_weapon_1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#6", "name2": "avg_npc_064_weapon_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  一些程序上的瑣事罷了，花不了多少功夫。", "name": "瑪嘉烈"}, "figure_art": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#6"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#6", "name2": "avg_npc_064_weapon_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......呵呵，你真的變了。", "name": "佐菲婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_064_weapon_1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  是因為那個叫“羅德島”的地方？你以前可根本不擅長那些文書工作。", "name": "佐菲婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_064_weapon_1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  還記得你剛報名成為騎士的時候嗎？獨立騎士瑪嘉烈·臨光，總是把各種證件和手續搞混......", "name": "佐菲婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_064_weapon_1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#6", "name2": "avg_npc_064_weapon_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  嗯......那時候多虧了有你，姑母。", "name": "瑪嘉烈"}, "figure_art": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#6"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#6", "name2": "avg_npc_064_weapon_1#6", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  唉......瑪莉婭那丫頭也就算了，你年紀不是和我差不多嗎？", "name": "佐菲婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_064_weapon_1#6"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  以前花了那麼大力氣讓你習慣直呼其名，怎麼幾年沒見，又變回去了？", "name": "佐菲婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_064_weapon_1#6"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  難道我們生疏了？嗯？", "name": "佐菲婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_064_weapon_1#6"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#6", "name2": "avg_npc_064_weapon_1#6", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......呵呵，沒有的事，佐菲婭。我只是很久沒和家人這樣面對面交流了。", "name": "瑪嘉烈"}, "figure_art": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#6"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你是來探望叔叔的嗎？", "name": "瑪嘉烈"}, "figure_art": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#6"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#6", "name2": "avg_npc_064_weapon_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  嗯......他還在工作嗎？", "name": "佐菲婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_064_weapon_1#5"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_148_nearl_ns_1", "name2": "avg_npc_064_weapon_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  還沒回。", "name": "瑪嘉烈"}, "figure_art": "char_148_nearl_ns_1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_148_nearl_ns_1", "name2": "avg_npc_064_weapon_1#6", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......瑪恩納他......", "name": "佐菲婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_064_weapon_1#6"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_148_nearl_ns_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_064_weapon_1#6", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 134, 